name: Missbrisolo (Brianna Torres) - Cosplay Superstar
description:
Missbrisolo (Real Name Brianna Torres) is TikTok content creator and social media personality best known for her self-titled account. She uploads videos of cosplay modeling, dancing, and lip syncing to popular songs. She has over 3 million followers. Born on February 28, 2000, Missbrisolo hails from , United States. As in 2023, Missbrisolo's age is 23 years.

Trained on 1.5 base model but exmples are from Consistent Factor, Realistic Vision and Analog Madness.

Notes: Unprompted it will make her a redhead, as she was in all the images, but it makes it a more natural color. Adding "Redhead" to the prompt will create the vibrant color she wears. Additionally, on some close-up, the system will include stray hairs on her face, due to varying hairstyles in the training dataset. Those might need to be inpainted out, but it is a simple solution if it occurs

Please drop me a comment if you have any suggestions/criticism/comments/request for the next model.
